tile sites-tile-name-header"><div dir="ltr"><div style="text-align:center"><span style="background-color:transparent;font-size:10pt"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align:center"><span style="background-color:transparent"><font color="#ff0000" size="6">龜雖壽</font></span></div><div style="text-align:center"><span style="background-color:transparent"><font color="#ff0000" face="times new roman, serif" size="5">Quy Tuy Thọ </font></span></div><div style="text-align:center"><div style="text-align:right"><font size="4"><span style="background-color:transparent;font-family:SimSun">曹操 </span><span style="background-color:transparent">Tào Tháo</span></font></div>

</div></div></div><table cellspacing="0" class="sites-layout-hbox"><tbody><tr><td class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-content-1 sites-canvas-sidebar sites-layout-empty-tile"><div dir="ltr"><br /></div></td><td class="sites-layout-tile sites-tile-name-content-2"><div dir="ltr"><div align="center">

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border:none">
 <tbody><tr>
  <td style="padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top">
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">神龟虽寿，</font></span></p>
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">犹有竟时。</font></span></p>
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">腾蛇乘雾，</font></span></p>
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">终为土灰。</font></span></p>
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">老骥伏枥，</font></span></p>
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">志在千里。</font></span></p>
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">烈士暮年，</font></span></p>
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">壮心不已。</font></span></p>
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">盈缩之期，</font></span></p>
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">不但在天。</font></span></p>
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">养怡之福，</font></span></p>
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">可得永年。</font></span></p>
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">幸甚至哉，</font></span></p>
  <p><span lang="ZH-CN"><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">歌以咏志。</font></span></p>
  </td>
  <td style="padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" valign="top">
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Thần quy tuy thọ,</font></p>
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Do hữu cánh thì.</font></p>
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Đằng xà thừa vụ,</font></p>
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Chung vi thổ hôi.</font></p>
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Lão kí phục lịch,</font></p>
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Chí tại thiên lí.</font></p>
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Liệt sĩ mộ niên,</font></p>
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Tráng tâm bất dĩ.</font></p>
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Doanh súc chi kì,</font></p>
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Bất đãn tại thiên.</font></p>
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Dưỡng di chi phúc,</font></p>
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Khả đắc vĩnh niên.</font></p>
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Hạnh thậm chí tai,</font></p>
  <p><font face="times new roman, serif" size="4">Ca dĩ vịnh chí.</font></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</tbody></table>

